  <brief_title>Evaluating of the Efficacy and Safety of Vardenafil in Subjects With Erectile Dysfunction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-Label, Multi-Centre, Study of Levitra 10 mg Once a Day in Males With Erectile Dysfunction Was Carried Out in Four Centres Namely Lagos, Port Harcourt, Enuge and Maiduguri at Their University Teaching Hospitals</official_title>
